<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.10.3">
<l>paranta teyvamum pallula kumpaṭait taṉṟuṭa ṉēviḻuṅkik</l>
<l>karantu miḻntu kaṭanti ṭantatu kaṇṭun teḷiyakillīr</l>
<l>ciraṅka ḷāla mararva ṇaṅkun tirukkuru kūrataṉuḷ</l>
<l>paraṉṟiṟa maṉṟip pallulakīr teyva maṟṟillai pēcumiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who cannot understand although you have seen [him], along with creating the gods that are spread out</l>
<l>and many worlds, swallow [them], hide [them], spit [them] out, cross [them and] scoop [them] up,</l>
<l>apart from the highest form in Tirukkurukūr where the immortals</l>
<l>bow with [their] heads, o you of many worlds, there is no other god. Speak!</l> 
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
